'''The Crash''' was a [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] in [[Vlarnya]] on [[Courkrus]]. The pirates of the [[Khuiumin Survivors]] hung out there. The interior was decorated with chunks of [[Transparisteel/Legends|transparisteel]] and [[Quadanium steel/Legends|quadanium steel]], from [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] kills or crashes.

